projectGridLines.stationName: 12 th Wonder Research India Pvt Ltd
projectGridLines.title: GHG Accounting (Carbon Accounting)
projectGridLines.description:
Description: Work on developing and refining the existing GHG Accounting software.

Skill Sets:

  • Artificial Intelligence (AI)
  • Machine Learning (ML)
  • Software Development
  • Environmental Science
  • Data Analytics

Expected Learning:

  • Gain an in-depth understanding of carbon accounting principles and methodologies.
  • Develop strategies for achieving carbon neutrality.
  • Enhance skills in AI and ML as applied to environmental data.
  • Master the integration of software development with environmental objectives.
  • Learn to analyze and interpret carbon emissions data effectively.

Specific Courses Required for Project Execution:

  • DotNet for backend development.
  • Angular for front-end development.
  • CSS for styling and layout.
  • Svelte for building fast and reactive user interfaces.
  • Courses in Environmental Science and Carbon Management.
